The paper is about a new question answering model that combines information from evidence across multiple documents. This falls under the category of natural language processing and machine learning, which are covered by several sub-categories in arXiv CS. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as it covers topics related to natural language processing. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely categories as they cover topics related to machine learning and neural networks. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as it covers topics related to search and retrieval of information. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a possible category as it covers topics related to neural networks.
